This is a album website built with no database, 
which means once you put it on the web server folder, it will works

Features:
support Music,flash,swf
support image uploading and the mark of images
support image comment
...

UI:
The UI is designed and you may modify if you like

Code:
Jquery and Jquery waterfall plugin is used
css, Js and php is mixed, you may disapart them if you like
